1 AN ACT relating to the Department of Agriculture and declaring an emergency.
2 Be it enacted by the General Assembly of the Commonwealth of Kentucky:
3 Section 1. KRS 246.030 is amended to read as follows:
4 The department shall consist of:
5 (1) The Office of the Commissioner;
6 (2) The Office of Agricultural Marketing, which shall include the following:
7 (a) The Promotion and Development Division;
8 (b) The Farm Safety and Rural Health[Shows and Fairs] Division;
9 (c) The Livestock Division;
10 (d) The Plant Division;
11 (e) The Education and Outreach Division; and
12 (f) The Direct Farm Marketing Division;
13 (3) The Office for Consumer and Environmental Protection, which shall include the
14 following:
15 (a) The Division of Regulation and Inspection;
16 (b) The Division of Food Distribution; and
17 (c) The Division of Environmental Services;
18 (4) The Office of State Veterinarian, which shall include the following:
19 (a) The Division of Regulatory Field Services
20 (b) The Division of Animal Health Programs; and
21 (c) The Division of Emergency Preparedness and Response;
22 (5) The Office of Administrative Services, which shall include the following:
23 (a) The Division of Human Resources;
24 (b) The Division of Administrative Services; and
25 (c) The Division of Information Technology;
26 (6) The Office of Communications;
27 (7) The Office of Legal Services;
